{
  "type": "reflection",
  "content": {
    "tiles": [
      {
        "id": "kO6s8Hrp5dhDpkj4",
        "title": "Reflecting",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "AAGNSf",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>These last two lessons are are a small demo of a much larger unit that some researchers and teachers are working on together.</p><p>We want to know what you think, and what advice you have!</p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 2",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>Today&#x27;s date:</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 5",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>Who did you work with?</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 4",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>What did you find hard or confusing? What did you do to deal with that?</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 3",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>What was the most interesting or surprising?</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 7",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p><strong>What did you wish you could have done, or what other suggestions do you have to include in the unit?</strong></p>"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "Snt5qP7bZAKf0Zhu",
        "title": "Text 6",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<h2>Extension</h2><p>If you finished early, try these challenges!</p><p></p><p><strong>Can you think about a different solution?</strong></p><ul><li>If your gripper opens and closes gradually, can you make it have only two settings (0% closed and 100% closed)?</li><li>If your gripper only goes from 0% closed to 100% closed, can you make it open and close more gradu<strong>ally?</strong></li></ul><p><strong>There are three challenges. Drag the boxes below or use your handout to try one, two, or all three of them!</strong></p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "NBX26exQgUJEkyRY",
        "title": "Challenge 1: Plan It",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "F_Hzec",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Plan your solution. Use the sketch space below to draw or write your idea, even if you don&#x27;t know exactly what blocks to use.</p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Different Solution: Sketch Your Idea",
              "content": {
                "type": "Drawing",
                "objects": []
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "Rfnkfl48TZV2pQ0i",
        "title": "Challenge 2: Try It",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "OFHhgX",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Actually do it! Try to make the different solution by changing your old program.</p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 8",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Write here whether your team figured out another way or didn&#x27;t.</p><p>If you want, you can also write about your strategy, questions, or new ideas.</p>"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "Y7LHOfcdeNFHHa4z",
        "title": "Challenge 3: Compare Solutions",
        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "G4HjL6",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Use the Class Gallery or talk with your peers to find a group that found a different solution than your group.</p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "Text 9",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>Whose group found a different solution than yours?</p><p>What was different about it?</p>"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}